    "divine_story": {
      "type": "divine-brand-story",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/Preet-hero-image.jpg",
        "caption": "Our Story",
        "pull_quote": "\"…turning the label over and asking,<br>'but what's really in this?'\"",
        "heading": "",
        "text": "<p>Divine Ingredients began, as many good things do, with a simple habit. For Preet Bhullar, that question wasn't fleeting curiosity. With a background in microbiology and quality control, she knew exactly what to look for — and more importantly, what didn't belong.</p><p>So she set a new standard. One rooted in honesty, not marketing. Every ingredient is sourced with intention, tested with rigour, and chosen because it earns its place — not because it sounds good on a label.</p><p>As a women-owned brand, Divine Ingredients carries a quiet confidence — precise, uncompromising, yet deeply personal. Because when you know better, you choose better.</p>",
        "signature": "— <em>Preet Bhullar,</em> Founder",
        "button_label": "Read our story",
        "button_link": "shopify://pages/about-us",
        "cap_label": "Founded by",
        "cap_name": "Preet Bhullar",
        "cap_role": "Microbiologist & Founder",
        "padding_top": 96,
        "padding_bottom": 96,
        "margin_bottom": 48,
        "item_heading_font_size": 22
      }
